snippet.title: Shin Megami Tensei SNES English - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Patch: http://agtp.romhack.net/project.php?id=smt

An example of gameplay from the original Super Famicom version of Shin Megami Tensei with an English language patch.  It's a short video showing me walking around the Cathedral, getting  into a fight, then giving viewers a look through the COMP menus.  

This game is awesome I just never figured out where to go in the Cathedral!  I know I'm supposed to leave and go kill demons elsewhere but finding my way around the place is so boring with the constant demons attacking that I put the game down and haven't gone back to it.  Consequently I've never beaten this game.
